quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  20,38,jab hum ne tumhari walida ko ilhamkiya tha jo tumhe bataya jata hai
  20,39,( woh yeh tha ) ke usay ( yani moose ko ) sandooq mein rakho phir is ( sandooq ) ko darya mein daal do to darya usay kinare par daal day ga ( aur ) mera aur is ka dushman usay utha le ga. aur ( moose ) mein ne tum par apni taraf se mohabbat daal di hai ( is liye ke tum par meharbani ki jaye ) aur is liye ke tum mere samnay parwarish pao
  20,40,jab tumhari behan ( firaon ke haan ) gayi aur kehnay lagi ke mein tumhe aisa shakhs batau jo is ko paley. to ( is tareeq se ) hum ne tum ko tumhari maa ke paas pouncha diya taakay un ki ankhen thandhi hon aur woh ranj nah karen. aur tum ne 1 shakhs ko maar dala to hum ne tum ko gham se mukhlasi di aur hum ne tumhari ( kayi baar ) azmaish ki. phir tum kayi saal ahal Mudin mein thehray rahay. phir ae moose tum ( qabliyat risalat ke ) andazay par aa puhanche
  20,41,aur mein ne tum ko apne ( kaam ke ) liye banaya hai
  20,42,to tum aur tumhara bhai dono hamari nishanain le kar jao aur meri yaad mein susti nah karna
  20,43,dono firaon ke paas jao woh sarkash ho raha hai
  20,44,aur is se narmi se baat karna shayad woh ghhor kere ya dar jaye
  20,45,dono kehnay lagey ke hamaray perwar-digaar hamein khauf hai ke hum par ta-adi karne lagey ya ziyada sarkash hojaye
  20,46,khuda ne farmaya ke daro mat mein tumahray sath hon ( aur ) santa aur daikhta hon
  20,47,( acha ) to is ke paas jao aur kaho ke hum aap ke perwar-digaar ke beje hue hain to bani Israel ko hamaray sath jaane ki ijazat dijiye. aur inhen azaab nah kijiye. hum aap ke paas aap ke perwar-digaar ki taraf se nishani le kar aeye hain. aur jo hadaayat ki baat manay is ko salamti ho
  20,48,hamari taraf yeh wahi aayi hai ke jo jhutla-ay aur munhh phairay is ke liye azaab ( tayyar ) hai
  20,49,( gharz moose aur Haroon firaon ke paas gay ) is ne kaha ke moose tumhara perwar-digaar kon hai ?
  20,50,kaha ke hamara perwar-digaar woh hai jis ne har cheez ko is ki shakal vsort bakhsh phir raah dikhayi
  20,51,kaha to pehli jamaaton kakiya haal ?
